      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "Richard Carey, claim agent for\nthe Great Northern, is buzzing\nabout Sacred Heart hospital like a\nmosquito nowadays trying to in\nduce Milan wreck victims to accept\na little of the company's cash as\nsalve for their injuries.\n\n\nHe has managed to make several\nsettlements at figures running from\n800 to $500. All the sufferers have\nstrong cases against the company,\nas the road where the wreck has\noccurred has been officially con-\ndemned by the state track in\nSnectOr."
    }
